WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.470
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.510
be with y'all again today. I have a word

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:07.869
for you. This word is quite a bit; I

00:00:07.879 --> 00:00:09.110
don't know, I'll probably make it a

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:12.589
two-part series here again. But I was

00:00:12.599 --> 00:00:14.990
praying. First off, I want to

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.510
say this: I hope you had a Merry

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:19.150
Christmas. I hope you had good family

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:21.390
time. I hope you got your heart's

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:24.150
desires. You know, it's a

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:26.750
wonderful time of the year; God is so

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:29.990
faithful. I was praying on

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.190
Christmas night, and

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:36.270
the Lord said, 'I want you to get inside

00:00:36.280 --> 00:00:38.510
the car, and I want you to drive around

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:41.990
and pray.'So I got in the

00:00:41.990 --> 00:00:42.000
car—it

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.069
was about five in

00:00:45.069 --> 00:00:45.079
the morning—and

00:00:45.079 --> 00:00:46.510
he said, 'I want you to listen to the

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:49.790
song Prayer by Petra, the band Petra. I

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:52.270
want you to listen to it in prayer.'So I

00:00:52.280 --> 00:00:54.110
just put it on repeat and just kept

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:57.069
praying in the spirit and listening

00:00:57.079 --> 00:01:01.189
to Prayer by Petra and just driving

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:03.750
around in my

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.190
town. All of a sudden, the Lord just

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:10.310
opened my eyes to the spirit realm when

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:13.109
I was worshiping and singing and praying.

00:01:13.119 --> 00:01:15.670
I came home, and the Lord said, 'I want

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:18.710
you to pray with your wife.'So I told

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:20.149
my wife, 'We're going to pray, and

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:23.350
we need to pray together.'So I started

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:26.310
interceding, and the Lord showed me, just

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:29.390
like he always does, the calendars; he

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:32.389
shows me in visions things that are

00:01:32.399 --> 00:01:36.310
coming. In this one, I could see

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:38.510
into January really clearly. I could see

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:41.149
into February and March. I could see plots

00:01:41.159 --> 00:01:44.950
and plans of the wicked—of them plotting

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:47.149
things against the American people,

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:49.670
against America's elections, against a

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:51.990
lot of things,

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:55.630
interference.

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:58.190
I have to be careful with some of

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.910
it because I'm not

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.350
going to release all of that, but I'm

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:06.830
going to say it like this: I

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:10.350
heard the Spirit of the Lord say,

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:17.390
'Great grace will be poured out over

00:02:17.390 --> 00:02:17.400
2024—a

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:20.630
great

00:02:20.630 --> 00:02:20.640
grace.'I

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:24.030
saw a grace

00:02:24.040 --> 00:02:28.470
wave. I could see

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:31.830
it on January, February, March, April, and

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:34.790
May; there was an acceleration of great

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:39.030
grace. I saw a change in the spiritual

00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:41.110
atmosphere concerning

00:02:41.110 --> 00:02:41.120
finances—a

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:44.470
supernatural

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:47.750
outpouring of finances for the people

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.670
who are listening in the Body of Christ.

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:52.710
It's going to pour on the just and the

00:02:52.720 --> 00:02:54.830
unjust.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:57.509
I saw

00:02:57.519 --> 00:03:00.990
a

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:03.309
great wave of

00:03:03.319 --> 00:03:05.070
money

00:03:05.070 --> 00:03:05.080
in

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:11.750
2024. I

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:14.229
saw a

00:03:14.229 --> 00:03:14.239
diffusing

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:18.990
of another plot of a virus—a

00:03:18.990 --> 00:03:19.000
diffusing.

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:22.030
Now, I don't understand that, but

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:24.830
it was like it was going to try to be

00:03:24.840 --> 00:03:28.309
something that turned into nothing more

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.670
so than what the enemy was trying to in

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:32.270
store for

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:35.149
2024. It was like

00:03:35.159 --> 00:03:38.270
you let out a balloon.

00:03:38.280 --> 00:03:41.990
I saw going

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:45.750
into April even more of a

00:03:45.750 --> 00:03:45.760
grace

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:48.550
acceleration of finances. There

00:03:48.550 --> 00:03:48.560
was

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:51.949
something about praying over April,

00:03:51.959 --> 00:03:54.509
and I could hear the Lord Jesus Christ

00:03:54.519 --> 00:03:56.030
talking to me

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:58.670
when I was praying and

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:01.350
singing.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:04.069
He was over this great grace time. I

00:04:04.079 --> 00:04:07.229
could see he was anticipating something.

00:04:07.239 --> 00:04:10.710
He was watching over

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:12.910
America;

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:16.390
I could see him watching over

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:20.550
our land. He was looking at us with

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:24.110
anticipation, watching how we were

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:28.230
going to handle these finances, how we

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:31.830
were handling this window of

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:34.029
a grace explosion—what I'm going to

00:04:34.039 --> 00:04:38.270
call grace acceleration.

00:04:38.280 --> 00:04:40.990
I got clear

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:45.029
into... I could see the weather. I

00:04:45.039 --> 00:04:48.670
could see storms. I could see, as far

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:50.590
as spring goes, a normal

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:53.469
spring with an acceleration of

00:04:53.479 --> 00:04:54.469
long-track

00:04:54.479 --> 00:04:58.230
tornadoes. I saw the jet stream

00:04:58.240 --> 00:05:00.670
strengthening and

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:04.510
accelerating.

00:05:04.520 --> 00:05:05.830
I'm not a

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:07.550
meteorologist, so I'm just telling you

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:10.189
what I see. I saw that the storms

00:05:10.199 --> 00:05:12.790
would be long-track tornadoes in some

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:17.110
places that would be at a stronger

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:19.909
category than an EF5 that we've

00:05:19.919 --> 00:05:23.710
never seen before.

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:26.350
This is stuff that doesn't

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:28.629
necessarily have to happen; this is

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:31.590
stuff that we can pray over to stop.

00:05:31.590 --> 00:05:31.600
Because

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:33.710
I'm a prophetic intercessor, I'm

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:35.590
trying to tell you things that the Lord

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:37.950
shows me that we have authority over, that we can change through the power of prayer. Over the storms, we have authority. We are able to speak to the storms and tell them, 'Peace, be still.'When he's showing me about the long-track tornadoes and these major events of the jet stream speeding up, I don't understand all that, but I'm just telling you we have

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:39.790
authority over the storms and

00:05:39.790 --> 00:05:39.800
drought in major places.

00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:43.270
So,

00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:54.070
speak

00:06:10.199 --> 00:06:13.510
over

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:16.029
the rain, speaking to the rain to come

00:06:16.039 --> 00:06:18.430
over your area so that you have water for

00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:21.150
your land; it doesn't have to be that way.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:25.629
Going into... I

00:06:25.639 --> 00:06:31.029
saw Trump with major rallies, with seas

00:06:31.039 --> 00:06:33.469
of people coming to his

00:06:33.479 --> 00:06:37.510
rallies. I saw him speaking on a stage

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:40.710
with a white shirt, a red tie, and a blue

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:43.469
suit like he always wears. He

00:06:43.479 --> 00:06:46.150
was preaching, and what looked like

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:48.390
mountains were in the background. I don't know

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.430
where it was—maybe it

00:06:50.430 --> 00:06:50.440
was Arizona—but

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:52.550
there

00:06:52.550 --> 00:06:52.560
were

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:55.670
mountains on

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:01.430
the horizon. I could see

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:04.270
them, and he was speaking there. I

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:07.070
won't tell you what I saw trying

00:07:07.080 --> 00:07:09.749
to happen against him; we just

00:07:09.759 --> 00:07:11.749
need to pray for his protection. That's

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:14.150
all I will say. You will need to pray for

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:18.070
his protection in massive rallies.

00:07:24.919 --> 00:07:28.469
I saw it outdoors,

00:07:28.479 --> 00:07:30.990
a big crowd

00:07:30.990 --> 00:07:31.000
and

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:33.070
mountains.

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:35.950
Going

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:39.430
into

00:07:39.440 --> 00:07:46.189
2025 again, I saw

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:48.670
something

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:51.629
like the great Hoover

00:07:51.639 --> 00:07:56.230
Dam in the Las Vegas, Nevada area. This was

00:07:56.240 --> 00:08:02.469
like a massive, thick, slate wall of

00:08:02.479 --> 00:08:07.070
something that looked as dark as

00:08:07.070 --> 00:08:07.080
onyx.

00:08:07.080 --> 00:08:10.469
Again, I saw it at the end of December

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:14.550
going into January.

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:18.670
It looked like it was

00:08:18.670 --> 00:08:18.680
impenetrable.

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:22.390
The blackness was the darkest black

00:08:22.400 --> 00:08:25.710
I've ever seen before. It went up

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:28.629
on a wall like this, and

00:08:28.639 --> 00:08:30.990
you could not see

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:34.029
through it.

00:08:34.029 --> 00:08:34.039
It

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:34.790
was

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:38.949
like

00:08:38.959 --> 00:08:41.149
crude oil behind it.

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:43.469
The more I

00:08:43.479 --> 00:08:45.750
was looking into

00:08:45.760 --> 00:08:47.389
January,

00:08:47.399 --> 00:08:49.070
February,

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:54.070
March, and April, all of a sudden it split.

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:56.710
What was blackest through those

00:08:56.720 --> 00:09:02.269
months had a bit of a green

00:09:02.279 --> 00:09:05.870
start to come upon the grass.

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:07.750
There were some trees I could see,

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:11.389
but then there was

00:09:11.399 --> 00:09:14.990
thick, thick black all on top of

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:19.949
these trees in March, April,

00:09:19.959 --> 00:09:22.389
and May of

00:09:22.399 --> 00:09:24.750
2025.

00:09:24.760 --> 00:09:27.389
I kept focusing on it

00:09:27.389 --> 00:09:27.399
because

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:28.829
I

00:09:28.829 --> 00:09:28.839
was

00:09:28.839 --> 00:09:31.590
like, 'Lord, why am I seeing this darkness

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:35.550
all on this timeframe?'But I

00:09:35.550 --> 00:09:35.560
saw Trump crying,

00:09:35.560 --> 00:09:38.910
hearing the word 'depression'—a Great

00:09:38.920 --> 00:09:43.310
Depression. Then I saw Trump in

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:46.430
the Oval Office, and he was

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:50.269
crying. He had his hands down on his

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:53.269
head at his desk in the Oval

00:09:53.279 --> 00:09:56.590
Office. This is another

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:58.710
thing we should pray over.

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:02.310
I'm not trying to get political; I'm

00:10:02.320 --> 00:10:05.550
just telling you what I saw.

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:15.949
He was crying and asking for mercy.

00:10:15.959 --> 00:10:18.750
He was crying out for mercy concerning

00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:21.910
America, and he was interceding. But it

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:25.430
was a different type of Trump: he was

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:29.990
skinnier, for one, and he looked

00:10:29.990 --> 00:10:30.000
worn

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:35.030
out, per se. But he

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:37.110
was broken to the point where he was

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:40.870
interceding. All of a sudden, I saw

00:10:40.880 --> 00:10:44.350
pastors in the Oval Office with him,

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:47.509
walking around praying.

00:10:47.519 --> 00:10:50.430
He had called for people to pray

00:10:50.440 --> 00:10:52.829
with him, and I could see these

00:10:52.829 --> 00:10:52.839
men—they

00:10:52.839 --> 00:10:54.829
weren't just standing there behind him like

00:10:54.839 --> 00:10:56.710
I've seen in pictures before;

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:01.670
they were actually pacing and

00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:05.350
interceding in the Oval Office, praying

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:07.949
in the spirit.

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:13.269
I saw a

00:11:13.269 --> 00:11:13.279
man—I

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:15.949
believe

00:11:15.959 --> 00:11:18.949
he's a pastor from somewhere—who had a

00:11:18.949 --> 00:11:18.959
bald

00:11:18.959 --> 00:11:21.230
head and hair on the

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:28.389
sides. He

00:11:28.399 --> 00:11:31.870
was a tall man,

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.350
very

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:38.150
slender in my opinion—probably

00:11:38.150 --> 00:11:38.160
240 or

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:43.030
250

00:11:43.030 --> 00:11:43.040
pounds.

00:11:43.040 --> 00:11:47.030
He was walking back and forth praying,

00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:47.040
wearing

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:49.990
a gray suit, a white shirt,

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:52.670
and no tie.

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:56.870
He was praying in there

00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:58.670
with

00:12:00.910 --> 00:12:00.920
Holy

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:04.750
Ghost

00:12:06.230 --> 00:12:06.240
energy.

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:09.190
The tears were just flowing down his

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:11.389
face when he was interceding for the

00:12:11.399 --> 00:12:15.069
nation. All of a sudden, I

00:12:15.069 --> 00:12:15.079
saw something

00:12:15.079 --> 00:12:19.310
very interesting. You

00:12:19.310 --> 00:12:19.320
know

00:12:19.320 --> 00:12:22.069
the paddles

00:12:22.069 --> 00:12:22.079
you

00:12:22.079 --> 00:12:23.990
use

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:26.509
to shock somebody to wake them

00:12:26.519 --> 00:12:31.550
up? I saw those hit the nation of

00:12:31.560 --> 00:12:35.629
America. I saw shockwaves go over

00:12:35.639 --> 00:12:38.069
the

00:12:38.079 --> 00:12:41.310
land, pulses.

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:44.310
I could see the shocks

00:12:44.310 --> 00:12:44.320
again—boom—and

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:47.189
I could see it rippling across

00:12:47.199 --> 00:12:51.150
the land. All of that black started

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:53.750
to move. There was a thick black that

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:57.230
started looking like waves of

00:12:57.240 --> 00:13:02.509
energy moving across the soil of

00:13:02.519 --> 00:13:05.310
America as this prayer was going on in

00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:06.910
the White

00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:09.590
House. Then all of a sudden, the Lord

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:13.629
said, 'Look.'I saw toward the

00:13:13.639 --> 00:13:18.790
North Pole, and I saw a light that

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:20.389
looked like a

00:13:20.399 --> 00:13:23.949
match. All of a sudden, the black

00:13:23.959 --> 00:13:27.310
was all over the world at this time.

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:34.590
If you were to take an egg

00:13:37.069 --> 00:13:37.079
and

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:42.670
put pressure from the inside out, like

00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:45.949
a chick breaking forth—that's the way

00:13:45.959 --> 00:13:49.189
this dome, which was

00:13:49.189 --> 00:13:49.199
a half-sphere

00:13:49.199 --> 00:13:53.590
over

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:56.910
this area, was breaking. The light was like

00:13:56.920 --> 00:13:59.829
a

00:13:59.839 --> 00:14:03.230
match, and all of a sudden this

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:05.470
energy—Holy

00:14:05.480 --> 00:14:07.150
Ghost

00:14:07.160 --> 00:14:08.910
energy—took

00:14:08.920 --> 00:14:12.470
it and exploded that blackness

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:16.310
off. It started to fall in pieces

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:18.590
like an

00:14:18.600 --> 00:14:20.870
eggshell

00:14:20.880 --> 00:14:24.030
shattering.

00:14:25.759 --> 00:14:27.749
All of a sudden, that

00:14:27.759 --> 00:14:30.030
anointing, that glow, that light from this

00:14:30.040 --> 00:14:32.470
match... it was the most

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:35.189
intense light I've ever seen,

00:14:35.199 --> 00:14:38.150
similar to what's at the Father's throne.

00:14:38.160 --> 00:14:40.389
It was at a center, but

00:14:40.399 --> 00:14:42.829
there was light upon light around it

00:14:42.839 --> 00:14:45.990
from the north. It split this black

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:49.069
out and exploded, and all of a sudden

00:14:49.079 --> 00:14:53.269
that light started sending rays of light

00:14:53.279 --> 00:14:56.110
through that eggshell-looking

00:14:56.110 --> 00:14:56.120
thing—this

00:14:56.120 --> 00:14:58.710
membrane, I'll call it.

00:14:58.710 --> 00:14:58.720
It

00:14:58.720 --> 00:15:00.670
started to split, and the light

00:15:00.680 --> 00:15:03.069
started shining all through

00:15:03.079 --> 00:15:06.710
it. Then the light started to spread.

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:08.749
I couldn't figure out what

00:15:08.759 --> 00:15:10.629
that was, but that's what I saw when I

00:15:10.639 --> 00:15:13.749
was praying. It

00:15:13.749 --> 00:15:13.759
was

00:15:13.759 --> 00:15:16.430
quite

00:15:16.440 --> 00:15:19.030
